DECLARE @InsertAuditID BIGINT = ?;

WITH PerQualifications AS 
(
SELECT 
pq.qualification_id AS QualificationID
, COALESCE(pqt.name, 'N/A') AS Accreditation
, COALESCE(pq.title, '') AS AreaOfStudy
, COALESCE(pq.start_date, '9999-12-31') AS AccreditationDate
, COALESCE(pq.comments, '') AS Comments
, CAST(HASHBYTES('MD5',
(SELECT pq.qualification_id
      , COALESCE(pqt.name, 'N/A') Accreditation
      , pq.title
      , pq.start_date
      , pq.comments FOR XML RAW)) AS BINARY(16)) AS RowHash
FROM dbo.PER_QUALIFICATIONS_B0 pq
LEFT JOIN dbo.PER_QUALIFICATION_TYPES_B0 pqt ON pq.qualification_type_id = pqt.qualification_type_id
WHERE pq.person_id IS NOT NULL AND (pq.BaseCreatedDate > ? OR pqt.BaseCreatedDate > ?)
)

SELECT *
, @InsertAuditID AS InsertAuditID  
FROM PerQualifications pq
WHERE NOT EXISTS
(
    SELECT 1
    FROM dbo.AccreditationBN abn
    WHERE pq.QualificationID = abn.QualificationID
);

DECLARE @InsertAuditID BIGINT = ?;

WITH Assessment AS 
(
SELECT 
 DISTINCT PAC.segment1 as AssessmentType,
  PAC.segment3 as AssessmentBand,
( coalesce(PAC.segment1,'') + case when PAC.segment1 is not null or PAC.segment3 is not null then   '_' end  + coalesce (PAC.segment3,'')) AS  AssessmentID 
, CAST(HASHBYTES('MD5',
(SELECT PAC.segment1 as AssessmentType,
  PAC.segment3 as AssessmentBand,
( coalesce(PAC.segment1,'') + case when PAC.segment1 is not null or PAC.segment3 is not null then   '_' end  + coalesce (PAC.segment3,'')) AS  AssessmentID FOR XML RAW)) AS BINARY(16)) AS RowHash
FROM dbo.PER_ANALYSIS_CRITERIA_B0 PAC
     LEFT JOIN dbo.FND_ID_FLEX_STRUCTURES_TL_B0 FIFST
        ON PAC.id_flex_num = FIFST.id_flex_num
WHERE  FIFST.id_flex_structure_name='Assessment -' AND (pac.BaseCreatedDate > ? OR FIFST.BaseCreatedDate > ?)
)

SELECT *
, @InsertAuditID AS InsertAuditID  
FROM Assessment pq
WHERE NOT EXISTS
(
    SELECT 1
    FROM dbo.AssessmentBN abn
    WHERE pq.AssessmentID = abn.AssessmentID
);

UPDATE dbo.AssignmentBN SET 
	ExpirationDate	= ?,
	BaseEndDate	=  ?,
	RowStatus	= 'H',
	BaseModifiedDate	= GETDATE(),
	UpdateAuditID	= ?
WHERE
	AssignmentID	= ? AND 
	BaseEndDate	= '9999-12-31' AND
	RowStatus	= 'A' AND
	Deleted IS NULL

UPDATE dbo.AssignmentBN SET
	RowStatus = 'H',
	BaseEndDate = ?,
	BaseModifiedDate = GETDATE(),
	UpdateAuditID = ?
WHERE
	AssignmentID = ? AND 
	BaseEndDate = '9999-12-31' AND 
	RowStatus = 'A' AND
	Deleted IS NULL

DECLARE @InsertAuditID bigint = ?;

SELECT 
	vabn.*,
	'SCD' AS Operation,
	@InsertAuditID AS InsertAuditID 
FROM dbo.vAssignmentBN AS vabn WITH (NOLOCK)
WHERE
	EXISTS
	(
		SELECT 1
		FROM dbo.AssignmentBN AS abn WITH (NOLOCK)
		WHERE
			vabn.AssignmentID = abn.AssignmentID AND 
			vabn.EffectiveStartDate = abn.EffectiveStartDate AND
			ISNULL(vabn.SecondaryRateStartDate, '1900-01-01') = ISNULL(abn.SecondaryRateStartDate, '1900-01-01') AND --GG
			vabn.BaseEndDate = '9999-12-31' AND
			vabn.RowHash <> abn.RowHash AND 
			abn.RowStatus = 'A' AND 
			COALESCE(abn.BaseEndDate, '9999-12-31') = '9999-12-31'
	)
UNION
SELECT 
	vabn.*,
	'Insert' AS Operation,
	@InsertAuditID AS InsertAuditID 
FROM dbo.vAssignmentBN AS vabn WITH (NOLOCK)
WHERE
	NOT EXISTS 
	(
		SELECT 1
		FROM dbo.AssignmentBN AS abn WITH (NOLOCK)
		WHERE
			vabn.AssignmentID = abn.AssignmentID AND 
			vabn.BaseEffectiveDate = abn.BaseEffectiveDate 
	)

DECLARE @InsertAuditID bigint = ?;
DECLARE @LastProcessedDate datetime = ?;

;WITH Assignments AS
(
	SELECT
		*,
		CASE
			WHEN BaseEndDate = '9999-12-31' OR BaseEndDate >= CAST(GETDATE() AS DATE) THEN 'A'
			ELSE 'H'
		END AS RowStatus,
		@InsertAuditID AS InsertAuditID
	FROM
		dbo.vAssignmentBN
)
SELECT
	*
FROM
	Assignments
WHERE
	(Assignments.AssignmentBaseCreatedDate > @LastProcessedDate OR
	Assignments.AssignmentStatusBaseCreatedDate > @LastProcessedDate OR
	Assignments.PeopleBaseCreatedDate > @LastProcessedDate OR
	Assignments.PayBaseCreatedDate > @LastProcessedDate OR
	Assignments.SuppliersBaseCreatedDate > @LastProcessedDate OR  
	Assignments.PeopleGroupsBaseCreatedDate > @LastProcessedDate OR
	Assignments.AnalysisBaseCreatedDate > @LastProcessedDate OR
	Assignments.AnalysisCriteriaBaseCreatedDate > @LastProcessedDate OR
	Assignments.FlexStructureBaseCreatedDate > @LastProcessedDate)
	AND NOT EXISTS
	(
		SELECT 1
		FROM dbo.AssignmentBN AS abn 
		WHERE
			Assignments.AssignmentID = abn.AssignmentID 
			--Assignments.EffectiveStartDate = abn.EffectiveStartDate AND 
			--Assignments.ExpirationDate = abn.ExpirationDate
	);

DECLARE @FlexValueSetName varchar(60) = ?
DECLARE @FlexValue varchar(150) = ?
DECLARE @Description varchar(240) = ?
DECLARE @BaseCreatedDate datetime2 = ?
DECLARE @InsertAuditID bigint = ?
DECLARE @RowHash binary(16) = ?

IF NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM dbo.FlexValuesLookupB10 WHERE FlexValueSetName = @FlexValueSetName AND FlexValue = @FlexValue AND [Description] = @Description)
	BEGIN
		INSERT INTO dbo.FlexValuesLookupB10
		(
			FlexValueSetName,
			FlexValue,
			[Description],
			BaseEffectiveDate,
			BaseEndDate,
			Deleted,
			RowStatus,
			BaseCreatedDate,
			InsertAuditID,
			RowHash
		)
		VALUES
		(
			@FlexValueSetName,
			@FlexValue,
			@Description,
			GETDATE(),
			'9999-12-31',
			NULL,
			'A',
			@BaseCreatedDate,
			@InsertAuditID,
			@RowHash
		)
	END

UPDATE dbo.FlexValuesLookupB10 SET
	BaseEndDate	= GETDATE(),
	Deleted		= NULL,
	RowStatus	= 'H'
WHERE
	FlexValueSetName	= ? AND
	FlexValue		= ? AND
	RowStatus	= 'A'

DECLARE @InsertAuditID bigint = ?
DECLARE @LastProcessedDate datetime = ?

SELECT
	t.FlexValueSetName,
	t.FlexValue,
	t.[Description],
	GETDATE() AS BaseEffectiveDate,
	'9999-12-31' AS BaseEndDate,
	NULL AS Deleted,
	'A' AS RowStatus,
	GETDATE() AS BaseCreatedDate,
	@InsertAuditID AS InsertAuditID,
	CAST(HASHBYTES('MD5', (SELECT t.FlexValueSetName, t.FlexValue, t.[Description] FOR XML RAW)) AS BINARY(16)) AS RowHash
FROM
	(SELECT 
		UPPER(fvs.flex_value_set_name) AS FlexValueSetName,
		UPPER(fv.flex_value) AS FlexValue,
		UPPER(fvtl.[description]) AS [Description],
		ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY fvs.flex_value_set_name, fv.flex_value ORDER BY fvs.flex_value_set_name, fv.flex_value, fv.creation_date ASC) AS RowNumber
	FROM
		dbo.FND_FLEX_VALUES_B0 AS fv WITH (NOLOCK)
		INNER JOIN
		dbo.FND_FLEX_VALUE_SETS_B0 AS fvs WITH (NOLOCK)
			ON	fv.flex_value_set_id = fvs.flex_value_set_id
		INNER JOIN
		dbo.FND_FLEX_VALUES_TL_B0 AS fvtl WITH (NOLOCK)
			ON	fv.flex_value_id = fvtl.flex_value_id
	) AS t
WHERE
	t.RowNumber			= 1
	--AND t.FlexValueBaseCreatedDate	> @LastProcessedDate

SELECT
	FlexValueSetName,
	UPPER(FlexValue) AS FlexValue,
	RowHash
FROM
	dbo.FlexValuesLookupB10 WITH (NOLOCK)
WHERE
	RowStatus = 'A'

select * from (SELECT
	FlexValueSetName,
	UPPER(FlexValue) AS FlexValue,
	RowHash
FROM
	dbo.FlexValuesLookupB10 WITH (NOLOCK)
WHERE
	RowStatus = 'A') [refTable]
where [refTable].[FlexValueSetName] = ? and [refTable].[FlexValue] = ?

UPDATE dbo.PayGradeBn
SET RowStatus = 'H'
, BaseEndDate = ?
, BaseModifiedDate = GETDATE()
, UpdateAuditID = ?
WHERE GradeID = ? AND EffectiveStartDate = ? AND ExpirationDate = ?  AND RowStatus = 'A'

DECLARE @InsertAuditID BIGINT = ?;

SELECT vpgbn.*, CASE WHEN vpgbn.BaseEndDate = '9999-12-31' OR BaseEndDate >= CAST(GETDATE() AS DATE) THEN 'A'
ELSE 'H' END AS RowStatus
, @InsertAuditID AS InsertAuditID 
FROM vPayGradeBN vpgbn
WHERE 
--(vpgbn.PerGradesBaseCreatedDate > ? OR vpgbn.PayGradesRulesBaseCreatedDate > ?) AND -- Fix for secondary update
EXISTS
(
    SELECT 1
    FROM dbo.PayGradeBN pgbn
    WHERE vpgbn.GradeID = pgbn.GradeID AND vpgbn.EffectiveStartDate = pgbn.EffectiveStartDate AND vpgbn.ExpirationDate = pgbn.ExpirationDate AND vpgbn.RowHash != pgbn.RowHash AND pgbn.RowStatus = 'A'
);

SELECT vpgbn.*, CASE WHEN vpgbn.BaseEndDate = '9999-12-31' OR BaseEndDate >= CAST(GETDATE() AS DATE) THEN 'A'
ELSE 'H' END AS RowStatus
, @InsertAuditID AS InsertAuditID 
FROM vPayGradeBN vpgbn
WHERE (vpgbn.PerGradesBaseCreatedDate > ? OR vpgbn.PayGradesRulesBaseCreatedDate > ?)
AND NOT EXISTS
(
    SELECT 1
    FROM dbo.PayGradeBN pgbn
    WHERE vpgbn.GradeID = pgbn.GradeID AND vpgbn.EffectiveStartDate = pgbn.EffectiveStartDate AND vpgbn.ExpirationDate = pgbn.ExpirationDate

ELSE 'H' END AS RowStatus

);

DECLARE @InsertAuditID BIGINT = ? ;
WITH B0Query AS (
SELECT Pps.period_of_service_id,
      CASE WHEN  Lkp.meaning IS NULL 
	  THEN 'Unknown' ELSE   Lkp.meaning
	  END AS [Termination Reason],
       CASE WHEN Pps.attribute2 IS NULL THEN 'Unkown' ELSE Pps.attribute2 END AS [Eligible FOR Rehire Indicator],
       CASE
           WHEN Pps.attribute3 = 'Y' THEN
               'Yes'
           WHEN Pps.attribute3 = 'N' THEN
               'No'
           WHEN Pps.attribute3 IS NULL THEN
               'Unknown'
			   ELSE Pps.attribute3
       END AS [Two Week Notice Indicator],
       CASE
           WHEN Pps.attribute5 = 'Y' THEN
               'Yes'
           WHEN Pps.attribute5 = 'N' THEN
               'No'
           WHEN
           (
               Pps.attribute5 IS NULL
              
           ) THEN
               'Unknown'
			   ELSE   Pps.attribute5
       END AS [Regrettable Termination Indicator],
      CASE WHEN  Pps.attribute4 IS NULL THEN 'N/A' ELSE Pps.attribute4 END AS [Termination Comments],
       Pps.notified_termination_date AS [Termination Notified Date],
       Pps.attribute1 AS [Last Worked Date]--,

      -- 'N' AS Deleted,
  
FROM dbo.PER_PERIODS_OF_SERVICE_B0 Pps
    LEFT JOIN dbo.FND_LOOKUP_VALUES_B0 Lkp
        ON Pps.leaving_reason = Lkp.lookup_code
AND  Lkp.lookup_type = 'LEAV_REAS'
      AND Lkp.deleted = 'N'
      AND Lkp.view_application_id = 3
WHERE (Lkp.BaseCreatedDate> ?  OR Pps.BaseCreatedDate>?)
AND Pps.actual_termination_date IS NOT NULL
AND Pps.period_of_service_id NOT IN     (
       SELECT DISTINCT [PeriodofServiceID] FROM TerminationBN
  ))
 SELECT A.period_of_service_id,
        A.[Termination Reason],
        A.[Eligible FOR Rehire Indicator],
        A.[Two Week Notice Indicator],
        A.[Regrettable Termination Indicator],
        A.[Termination Comments],
        A.[Termination Notified Date],
        A.[Last Worked Date],
		
		 CAST(HASHBYTES('MD5',
		  (SELECT A.period_of_service_id,
        A.[Termination Reason],
        A.[Eligible FOR Rehire Indicator],
        A.[Two Week Notice Indicator],
        A.[Regrettable Termination Indicator],
        A.[Termination Comments],
        A.[Termination Notified Date],
        A.[Last Worked Date] FOR XML RAW)) AS BINARY(16)) AS RowHash,
        @InsertAuditID AS InsertAuditID
		FROM B0Query A

WITH PerQualifications AS

, COALESCE(pqt.name, 'N/A') AS Accreditation
, COALESCE(pq.title, '') AS AreaOfStudy
, COALESCE(pq.start_date, '9999-12-31') AS AccreditationDate
, COALESCE(pq.comments, '') AS Comments

)

DECLARE @InsertAuditID BIGINT = ?;

WITH Assessment AS 
(
SELECT 
 DISTINCT PAC.segment1 as AssessmentType,
  PAC.segment3 as AssessmentBand,
( coalesce(PAC.segment1,'') + case when PAC.segment1 is not null or PAC.segment3 is not null then   '_' end  + coalesce (PAC.segment3,'')) AS  AssessmentID 
, CAST(HASHBYTES('MD5',
(SELECT PAC.segment1 as AssessmentType,
  PAC.segment3 as AssessmentBand,
( coalesce(PAC.segment1,'') + case when PAC.segment1 is not null or PAC.segment3 is not null then   '_' end  + coalesce (PAC.segment3,'')) AS  AssessmentID FOR XML RAW)) AS BINARY(16)) AS RowHash
FROM dbo.PER_ANALYSIS_CRITERIA_B0 PAC
     LEFT JOIN dbo.FND_ID_FLEX_STRUCTURES_TL_B0 FIFST
        ON PAC.id_flex_num = FIFST.id_flex_num
WHERE  FIFST.id_flex_structure_name like  'Assessment%' AND (pac.BaseCreatedDate > ? OR FIFST.BaseCreatedDate > ?)
)

SELECT *

FROM Assessment pq

(

    FROM dbo.AssessmentBN abn
    WHERE pq.AssessmentID = abn.AssessmentID
);

DECLARE @FlexValueSetName varchar(60) = ?
DECLARE @FlexValue varchar(150) = ?
DECLARE @Description varchar(240) = ?
DECLARE @BaseCreatedDate datetime2 = ?
DECLARE @InsertAuditID bigint = ?
DECLARE @RowHash binary(16) = ?

IF NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM dbo.FlexValuesLookupB10 WHERE FlexValueSetName = @FlexValueSetName AND FlexValue = @FlexValue AND [Description] = @Description)
	BEGIN
		INSERT INTO dbo.FlexValuesLookupB10
		(
			FlexValueSetName,
			FlexValue,
			[Description],
			BaseEffectiveDate,
			BaseEndDate,
			Deleted,
			RowStatus,
			BaseCreatedDate,
			InsertAuditID,
			RowHash
		)
		VALUES
		(
			@FlexValueSetName,
			@FlexValue,
			@Description,
			GETDATE(),
			'9999-12-31',
			NULL,
			'A',
			@BaseCreatedDate,
			@InsertAuditID,
			@RowHash
		)
	END

UPDATE dbo.FlexValuesLookupB10 SET
	BaseEndDate	= GETDATE(),
	Deleted		= NULL,
	RowStatus	= 'H'
WHERE
	FlexValueSetName	= ? AND
	FlexValue		= ? AND
	RowStatus	= 'A'

DECLARE @InsertAuditID bigint = ?
DECLARE @LastProcessedDate datetime = ?

SELECT
	t.FlexValueSetName,
	t.FlexValue,
	t.[Description],
	GETDATE() AS BaseEffectiveDate,
	'9999-12-31' AS BaseEndDate,
	NULL AS Deleted,
	'A' AS RowStatus,
	GETDATE() AS BaseCreatedDate,
	@InsertAuditID AS InsertAuditID,
	CAST(HASHBYTES('MD5', (SELECT t.FlexValueSetName, t.FlexValue, t.[Description] FOR XML RAW)) AS BINARY(16)) AS RowHash
FROM
	(SELECT 
		UPPER(fvs.flex_value_set_name) AS FlexValueSetName,
		UPPER(fv.flex_value) AS FlexValue,
		UPPER(fvtl.[description]) AS [Description],
		ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY fvs.flex_value_set_name, fv.flex_value ORDER BY fvs.flex_value_set_name, fv.flex_value, fv.creation_date ASC) AS RowNumber
	FROM
		dbo.FND_FLEX_VALUES_B0 AS fv WITH (NOLOCK)
		INNER JOIN
		dbo.FND_FLEX_VALUE_SETS_B0 AS fvs WITH (NOLOCK)
			ON	fv.flex_value_set_id = fvs.flex_value_set_id
		INNER JOIN
		dbo.FND_FLEX_VALUES_TL_B0 AS fvtl WITH (NOLOCK)
			ON	fv.flex_value_id = fvtl.flex_value_id
	) AS t
WHERE
	t.RowNumber			= 1
	--AND t.FlexValueBaseCreatedDate	> @LastProcessedDate

SELECT
	FlexValueSetName,
	UPPER(FlexValue) AS FlexValue,
	RowHash
FROM
	dbo.FlexValuesLookupB10 WITH (NOLOCK)
WHERE
	RowStatus = 'A'

select * from (SELECT
	FlexValueSetName,
	UPPER(FlexValue) AS FlexValue,
	RowHash
FROM
	dbo.FlexValuesLookupB10 WITH (NOLOCK)
WHERE
	RowStatus = 'A') [refTable]
where [refTable].[FlexValueSetName] = ? and [refTable].[FlexValue] = ?

DECLARE @InsertAuditID BIGINT = ?;

WITH AllRecords AS 
(
SELECT 
	vabn.*,
	'SCD' AS Operation,
	@InsertAuditID AS InsertAuditID
FROM dbo.vPayGradeBN AS vabn WITH (NOLOCK)
WHERE
	EXISTS
	(
		SELECT 1
		FROM dbo.PayGradeBN AS abn WITH (NOLOCK)
		WHERE
			vabn.GradeID = abn.GradeID AND 
			vabn.EffectiveStartDate = abn.EffectiveStartDate AND
			vabn.BaseEffectiveDate = abn.BaseEffectiveDate AND 
			vabn.BaseEndDate = '9999-12-31' AND
			vabn.RowHash <> abn.RowHash AND 
			abn.RowStatus = 'A' AND COALESCE(abn.BaseEndDate, '9999-12-31') = '9999-12-31'
	)
UNION
SELECT 
	vabn.*,
	'Insert' AS Operation,
	@InsertAuditID AS InsertAuditID
FROM dbo.vPayGradeBN AS vabn WITH (NOLOCK)
WHERE
	NOT EXISTS 
	(
		SELECT 1
		FROM dbo.PayGradeBN AS abn WITH (NOLOCK)
		WHERE
			vabn.GradeID = abn.GradeID AND 
			vabn.BaseEffectiveDate = abn.BaseEffectiveDate 
	)
)
SELECT * FROM AllRecords
WHERE Operation IS NOT NULL

UPDATE dbo.PositionBN
   SET [ExpirationDate] = ?
      ,[BaseEndDate]	   = ?
      ,[RowStatus]		   = 'H'
      ,[BaseModifiedDate]  = GETDATE()
      ,[UpdateAuditID]	   = ?
WHERE PositionID = ? AND (BaseEndDate= '9999-12-31' OR BaseEndDate > GETDATE())
AND RowStatus = 'A' and Deleted IS NULL

UPDATE dbo.PositionBn
SET RowStatus = 'H'
, BaseEndDate = ?
, BaseModifiedDate = GETDATE()
, UpdateAuditID = ?
WHERE PositionID = ? AND BaseEndDate = '9999-12-31' AND RowStatus = 'A' AND Deleted IS NULL

DECLARE @InsertAuditID BIGINT = ?;

WITH AllRecords AS 
(
SELECT 
	vp.*,
'SCD' AS Operation
, @InsertAuditID AS InsertAuditID 
FROM dbo.vPositionBN vp
WHERE EXISTS
(
    SELECT 1
    FROM dbo.PositionBN  (NOLOCK)  AS pbn
    WHERE vp.PositionID = pbn.PositionID 
		  AND vp.EffectiveStartDate = pbn.EffectiveStartDate
		  AND vp.BaseEndDate = '9999-12-31'
		  AND vp.RowHash <> pbn.RowHash AND pbn.RowStatus = 'A' AND COALESCE(pbn.BaseEndDate, '9999-12-31') = '9999-12-31'
)
UNION ALL
SELECT
vp.*, 
'Insert' AS Operation
,  @InsertAuditID AS InsertAuditID 
FROM dbo.vPositionBN vp
WHERE NOT EXISTS 
(
    SELECT 1
    FROM dbo.PositionBN  (NOLOCK)  AS pbn
    WHERE vp.PositionID = pbn.PositionID AND vp.BaseEffectiveDate = pbn.BaseEffectiveDate 
)
)
, RemoveDuplicateOperation AS 
(
SELECT *, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY p.PositionID ORDER BY p.Operation) AS RowNumber 
FROM AllRecords p
)
SELECT 
r.* 
FROM RemoveDuplicateOperation r
WHERE r.Operation IS NOT NULL AND r.RowNumber = 1

DECLARE @InsertAuditID BIGINT = ?;
DECLARE @LastProcessedDate DATETIME = ?;

SELECT vp.*, CASE WHEN vp.BaseEndDate = '9999-12-31' OR BaseEndDate >= CAST(GETDATE() AS DATE) THEN 'A'
ELSE 'H' END AS RowStatus
, @InsertAuditID AS InsertAuditID
FROM vPositionBN vp
WHERE (vp.PositionsBaseCreatedDate > @LastProcessedDate OR vp.PerJobsBaseCreatedDate > @LastProcessedDate OR vp.PerPayBasesBaseCreatedDate > @LastProcessedDate OR vp.PositionStatusBaseCreatedDate > @LastProcessedDate OR vp.ADPJobBaseCreatedDate > @LastProcessedDate
			OR vp.JobGroupBaseCreatedDate > @LastProcessedDate OR vp.EEOBaseCreatedDate > @LastProcessedDate OR vp.FSLABaseCreatedDate > @LastProcessedDate)
AND NOT EXISTS
(
    SELECT 1
    FROM dbo.PositionBN pbn
    WHERE vp.PositionID = pbn.PositionID AND pbn.Deleted IS NULL
);

DECLARE @InsertAuditID bigint = ?
DECLARE @LastProcessedDate datetime = ?

;WITH B0Query AS
(
	SELECT
		Pps.PerPeriodsID AS period_of_service_id,
		CASE
			WHEN Lkp.meaning IS NULL THEN IIF(Pps.LeavingReason IS NULL, 'Unknown', 'Unknown (' + Pps.LeavingReason + ')')
			ELSE Lkp.meaning
		END AS [Termination Reason],
		CASE
			WHEN Lkp.attribute2 IS NULL THEN IIF(Pps.LeavingReason IS NULL, 'Unknown', 'Unknown (' + Pps.LeavingReason + ')')
			ELSE Lkp.attribute2
		END AS [Termination Type],
		CASE
			WHEN Pps.EligibleForRehireInd IS NULL THEN 'Unknown'
			ELSE Pps.EligibleForRehireInd
		END AS [Eligible FOR Rehire Indicator],
		CASE
			WHEN Pps.TwoWeekNoticeInd = 'Y' THEN 'Yes'
			WHEN Pps.TwoWeekNoticeInd = 'N' THEN 'No'
			WHEN Pps.TwoWeekNoticeInd IS NULL THEN 'Unknown'
			ELSE Pps.TwoWeekNoticeInd
		END AS [Two Week Notice Indicator],
		CASE
			WHEN Pps.RegrettableTerminationInd = 'Y' THEN 'Yes'
			WHEN Pps.RegrettableTerminationInd = 'N' THEN 'No'
			WHEN Pps.RegrettableTerminationInd IS NULL THEN 'Unknown'
			ELSE Pps.RegrettableTerminationInd
		END AS [Regrettable Termination Indicator],
		CASE
			WHEN Pps.TerminationComments IS NULL THEN 'N/A'
			ELSE Pps.TerminationComments
		END AS [Termination Comments],
		Pps.NotifiedTerminationDate AS [Termination Notified Date],
		Pps.LastWorkedDate AS [Last Worked Date]
	FROM
		dbo.PerPeriodsB10 AS Pps WITH (NOLOCK)
		LEFT JOIN
		dbo.FND_LOOKUP_VALUES_B0 AS Lkp WITH (NOLOCK)
			ON Pps.LeavingReason = Lkp.lookup_code AND
			Lkp.lookup_type = 'LEAV_REAS' AND
			Lkp.deleted = 'N' AND
			Lkp.view_application_id = 3
	WHERE
		(Lkp.BaseCreatedDate > @LastProcessedDate OR Pps.BaseCreatedDate > @LastProcessedDate OR Pps.BaseModifiedDate > @LastProcessedDate)
		AND Pps.ActualTerminationDate IS NOT NULL
		AND Pps.PerPeriodsID NOT IN
		(SELECT DISTINCT [PeriodofServiceID] FROM dbo.TerminationBN WITH (NOLOCK))
)
SELECT
	A.period_of_service_id,
	A.[Termination Reason],
	A.[Termination Type],
	A.[Eligible FOR Rehire Indicator],
	A.[Two Week Notice Indicator],
	A.[Regrettable Termination Indicator],
	A.[Termination Comments],
	A.[Termination Notified Date],
	A.[Last Worked Date],
	CAST(HASHBYTES('MD5',
		(SELECT
			A.period_of_service_id,
			A.[Termination Reason],
			A.[Termination Type],
			A.[Eligible FOR Rehire Indicator],
			A.[Two Week Notice Indicator],
			A.[Regrettable Termination Indicator],
			A.[Termination Comments],
			A.[Termination Notified Date],
			A.[Last Worked Date] FOR XML RAW)
		) AS BINARY(16)) AS RowHash,
	@InsertAuditID AS InsertAuditID
FROM
	B0Query AS A
